'''Kane Mihal''', a former street-thug, was known by his associates for his ostentatious clothing and boisterous demeanor in conversation. During confrontations, he often engaged in risky behavior to impress [[Gender/Legends|women]] he found appealing, if they were present. He booked passage aboard the ''[[Ananuru Express]]'' during the time the secret [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[RNA brainwashing virus]] was being auctioned. Throughout the journey, he demonstrated a lack of familiarity with dining etiquette, using incorrect utensils instead of acknowledging his inexperience. When [[Secesh Trant]] attempted to steal the [[Data-tape/Legends|datatape]] containing the virus's information, Mihal collaborated with members of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] to confront her.<ref name="Chal">{{ChallengeCite|72|Ananuru Express (article)}}</ref>

